    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for a Class II device with medium model influence. The CFD model is judged credible for its intended use of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. The relative hemolysis index predictions satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five operating points.",
